<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="description" content="Agro Sustentável - Cultivando o futuro com responsabilidade ambiental, econômica e social.">
<title>Agro Sustentável | Cultivando o Futuro</title>
<style>
  /* ============ RESET & BASE ============ */
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --verde-escuro: #1b4332;
    --verde-medio: #2d6a4f;
    --verde-claro: #52b788;
    --verde-suave: #b7e4c7;
    --terra: #7c5e3c;
    --terra-clara: #c9a27a;
    --dourado: #e9b949;
    --creme: #f8f5ee;
    --texto: #1a2e1f;
    --branco: #ffffff;
    --sombra: 0 10px 30px rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.12);
    --sombra-forte: 0 20px 50px rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.25);
    --transicao: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: var(--texto);
    background: var(--creme);
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
  a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
  ul { list-style: none; }
  .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

  /* ============ HEADER / NAV ============ */
  header {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%;
    background: rgba(248, 245, 238, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    z-index: 1000;
    transition: var(--transicao);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.08);
  }
  header.scrolled { box-shadow: var(--sombra); }
  nav {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 18px 24px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .logo {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--verde-escuro);
  }
  .logo-icon {
    width: 42px; height: 42px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--verde-claro), var(--verde-escuro));
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.4);
  }
  .logo-icon svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; fill: white; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; }
  .nav-links a {
    font-weight: 500; color: var(--texto); position: relative;
    transition: color var(--transicao);
  }
  .nav-links a::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -6px; left: 0;
    width: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--verde-claro);
    transition: width var(--transicao);
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--verde-medio); }
  .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }
  .btn-nav {
    background: var(--verde-escuro); color: white !important;
    padding: 10px 22px; border-radius: 30px;
    transition: var(--transicao);
  }
  .btn-nav:hover { background: var(--verde-medio); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-nav::after { display: none; }
  .menu-toggle {
    display: none; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
    width: 32px; height: 32px; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-around;
  }
  .menu-toggle span {
    display: block; height: 3px; background: var(--verde-escuro);
    border-radius: 2px; transition: var(--transicao);
  }

  /* ============ HERO ============ */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.15), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, rgba(233, 185, 73, 0.12), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f5ee 0%, #e8f1e4 100%);
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    padding: 120px 0 60px;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.08) 2px, transparent 2px),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(124, 94, 60, 0.06) 2px, transparent 2px);
    background-size: 60px 60px, 80px 80px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px; align-items: center; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.15); color: var(--verde-escuro);
    padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.3);
  }
  .hero-badge::before {
    content: '🌱'; font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--verde-escuro); margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  .hero h1 span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--verde-claro), var(--dourado));
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.15rem; color: #4a5a4e;
    margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 520px;
  }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
    padding: 14px 30px; border-radius: 30px;
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
    transition: var(--transicao); cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--verde-escuro); color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.3);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--verde-medio);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.4);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent; color: var(--verde-escuro);
    border-color: var(--verde-escuro);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--verde-escuro); color: white;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .hero-visual {
    position: relative; height: 500px;
    display: grid; place-items: center;
  }
  .hero-circle {
    width: 420px; height: 420px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--verde-claro), var(--verde-escuro));
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.35);
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .hero-circle::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, var(--verde-medio), var(--verde-claro));
  }
  .hero-circle::after {
    content: '🌾'; position: absolute;
    font-size: 8rem; top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
  }
  .floating-card {
    position: absolute; background: white;
    padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--sombra-forte);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .floating-card .icon {
    width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 12px;
    display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .card-1 { top: 10%; left: -20px; animation-delay: 0s; }
  .card-1 .icon { background: rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.15); }
  .card-2 { bottom: 15%; right: -10px; animation-delay: 2s; }
  .card-2 .icon { background: rgba(233, 185, 73, 0.2); }
  .card-3 { top: 50%; right: 10px; animation-delay: 4s; }
  .card-3 .icon { background: rgba(124, 94, 60, 0.15); }
  .floating-card strong { display: block; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--verde-escuro); }
  .floating-card small { color: #6b7a6e; font-size: 0.8rem; }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
  }

  /* ============ SECTIONS ============ */
  section { padding: 100px 0; }
  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block; color: var(--verde-medio);
    font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    color: var(--verde-escuro); font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .section-header p {
    max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;
    color: #5a6a5e; font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* ============ PILARES ============ */
  .pilares { background: white; }
  .pilares-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
  }
  .pilar-card {
    background: var(--creme);
    padding: 40px 32px; border-radius: 20px;
    transition: var(--transicao);
    border: 1px solid rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.06);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .pilar-card::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--verde-claro), var(--dourado));
    transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform var(--transicao);
  }
  .pilar-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: var(--sombra-forte);
    background: white;
  }
  .pilar-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .pilar-icon {
    width: 70px; height: 70px; border-radius: 18px;
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 2rem;
    transition: var(--transicao);
  }
  .pilar-card:hover .pilar-icon { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-5deg); }
  .pilar-amb .pilar-icon { background: rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.15); }
  .pilar-eco .pilar-icon { background: rgba(233, 185, 73, 0.2); }
  .pilar-soc .pilar-icon { background: rgba(124, 94, 60, 0.15); }
  .pilar-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--verde-escuro);
    margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .pilar-card p { color: #5a6a5e; }

  /* ============ PRÁTICAS ============ */
  .praticas {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--creme) 0%, #e8f1e4 100%);
  }
  .praticas-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .pratica-card {
    background: white; padding: 32px 28px;
    border-radius: 18px; transition: var(--transicao);
    border: 1px solid rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.08);
    position: relative;
  }
  .pratica-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: var(--sombra);
  }
  .pratica-num {
    position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 24px;
    font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800;
    color: rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.15);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .pratica-emoji {
    font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: var(--transicao);
  }
  .pratica-card:hover .pratica-emoji { transform: scale(1.2) rotate(10deg); }
  .pratica-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--verde-escuro);
    margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .pratica-card p { color: #5a6a5e; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  /* ============ STATS ============ */
  .stats {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--verde-escuro), var(--verde-medio));
    color: white; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .stats::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px, 60px 60px;
  }
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 40px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .stat-item { text-align: center; }
  .stat-number {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800; color: var(--dourado);
    line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ============ TECNOLOGIA ============ */
  .tecnologia { background: white; }
  .tech-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px; align-items: center;
  }
  .tech-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    color: var(--verde-escuro); margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .tech-content > p {
    color: #5a6a5e; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .tech-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; }
  .tech-item {
    display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 18px; background: var(--creme);
    border-radius: 14px; transition: var(--transicao);
    border-left: 3px solid transparent;
  }
  .tech-item:hover {
    background: #e8f1e4;
    border-left-color: var(--verde-claro);
    transform: translateX(6px);
  }
  .tech-item-icon {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: white; border-radius: 12px;
    display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.08);
  }
  .tech-item h5 {
    color: var(--verde-escuro); font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .tech-item p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #5a6a5e; }

  .tech-visual {
    position: relative; height: 480px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f1e4, #f8f5ee);
    border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden;
    display: grid; place-items: center;
  }
  .tech-visual::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 48%, rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.1) 49%, rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.1) 51%, transparent 52%),
      linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 48%, rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.1) 49%, rgba(82, 183, 136, 0.1) 51%, transparent 52%);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
  }
  .tech-icon-big {
    font-size: 10rem; position: relative; z-index: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 40px rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.2));
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .tech-orbit {
    position: absolute; width: 360px; height: 360px;
    border: 2px dashed rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
  }
  .tech-orbit::before, .tech-orbit::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute;
    width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: white; display: grid; place-items: center;
    box-shadow: var(--sombra);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .tech-orbit::before {
    content: '🛰️'; top: -25px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
  .tech-orbit::after {
    content: '🌡️'; bottom: -25px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
  @keyframes rotate {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  /* ============ CTA ============ */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dourado), var(--terra-clara));
    text-align: center; color: white;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-section::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 50%, rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.1), transparent 50%);
  }
  .cta-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--verde-escuro);
  }
  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 36px;
    color: rgba(27, 46, 31, 0.85);
  }
  .cta-content .btn-primary {
    background: var(--verde-escuro);
  }
  .cta-content .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--texto); }

  /* ============ FOOTER ============ */
  footer {
    background: var(--verde-escuro); color: #cfe3d5;
    padding: 70px 0 30px;
  }
  .footer-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 50px;
  }
  .footer-brand .logo { color: white; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .footer-brand p {
    color: #a8c5b0; font-size: 0.95rem;
    max-width: 320px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .social-links { display: flex; gap: 12px; }
  .social-links a {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    transition: var(--transicao);
  }
  .social-links a:hover {
    background: var(--verde-claro);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .social-links svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; fill: white; }
  .footer-col h4 {
    color: white; font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .footer-col ul { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .footer-col a {
    color: #a8c5b0; font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: var(--transicao);
  }
  .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--verde-claro); padding-left: 6px; }
  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-top: 24px; text-align: center;
    color: #7fa38a; font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* ============ ANIMAÇÕES SCROLL ============ */
  .fade-in {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }
  .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ============ RESPONSIVO ============ */
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .hero-grid, .tech-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .hero-visual { height: 400px; }
    .hero-circle { width: 320px; height: 320px; }
    .pilares-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .nav-links {
      position: fixed; top: 72px; right: -100%;
      flex-direction: column; background: white;
      width: 80%; max-width: 320px; height: calc(100vh - 72px);
      padding: 40px 30px; gap: 24px;
      box-shadow: -10px 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: right var(--transicao);
    }
    .nav-links.active { right: 0; }
    .menu-toggle { display: flex; }
    section { padding: 70px 0; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-cta { flex-direction: column; }
    .btn-primary, .btn-secondary { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
    .floating-card { padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .floating-card .icon { width: 36px; height: 36px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ============ HEADER ============ -->
<header id="header">
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="logo">
      <span class="logo-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 21.34l1.89.66.95-2.3c.48.17.98.3 1.34.3C19 20 22 3 22 3c-1 2-8 2.25-13 3.25S2 11.5 2 13.5s1.75 3.75 1.75 3.75C7 8 17 8 17 8z"/></svg>
      </span>
      AgroVerde
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <li><a href="#inicio">Início</a></li>
      <li><a href="#pilares">Pilares</a></li>
      <li><a href="#praticas">Práticas</a></li>
      <li><a href="#tecnologia">Tecnologia</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contato" class="btn-nav">Contato</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Menu">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero" id="inicio">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <span class="hero-badge">Cultivando o futuro</span>
        <h1>Agricultura que <span>respeita</span> a terra e alimenta o mundo</h1>
        <p>Unimos tradição, ciência e tecnologia para produzir alimentos com responsabilidade ambiental, viabilidade econômica e justiça social. O agro do amanhã começa hoje.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="#praticas" class="btn-primary">
            Conheça as práticas
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#pilares" class="btn-secondary">Nossos pilares</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="hero-circle"></div>
        <div class="floating-card card-1">
          <div class="icon">🌱</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Plantio Direto</strong>
            <small>Solo protegido</small>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="floating-card card-2">
          <div class="icon">☀️</div>
